column8: SUPER COMFORTABLE WITH SEAMLESS FABRIC - 100% Cotton A-shirts are being famous to be breathable, moisture and vapor absorber. Its fabric allows for all day wear during any type of activity as it keeps you comfortably dry. The seam less design benefits to Not Show Out from your top - Wicks off Moisture - Moves with the Body while being active in sports or in gym.

EXTREMELY FUNCTIONAL & EASE OF WEAR - This tank top is highly versatile. You can incorporate into just about any outfit. It can be tucked into dress pants, blazer or even pairing it with jeans for a more casual look. It can be worn within another pair of shirt, long sleeve cloths, jacket, and is even a good pair with your jacket suit if worn casually or informally.

FULL SHOULDER WITH HIGH NECKLINE STYLE DESIGN- Because of its versatility, it is extremely an indispensable item in your wardrobe. Its high neck design allows for more coverage great for wearing it by itself without another top with its full shoulder support that conceals bra straps for a conservative appearance. perfect under a shirt or even by itself.

MACHINE WASHABLE - EASY CARE - 100% Cotton shirts are the most convenient to care when it comes to maintenance. They can be machine warm washed, or can be tumbled dry low many times without shrinking or losing its fine soft and structure quality. Only use non-chlorine bleach to maintain its optimum softness.

SATISFACTION GUARANTEE- At Rosette good is never good enough! Customer satisfaction is our top priority. We offer a full 30 day money-back guarantee for every product that leaves our place. If you aren’t completely satisfied with your purchase, just send the product back our way and we promise to make it right.",[],"Rosette Women’s Sleeveless Undershirt - Cotton – High Neck, Full shoulder design","<div class=""a-section a-spacing-base variation-dropdown"" id=""variation_size_name"">

column8: This item fits true to size. These socks were built to for cushioned comfort and durability

PACT is obsessed with a big idea: clothes that make the world a better place. Socks with soul, altruistic underwear, and other everyday essentials made with fabrics that feel good and go easy on the environment. The best part: with every purchase, you help PACT make a positive change in our world. As our mission always has been, PACT is going all the way back to the source - our farmers. In India, PACT organic cotton is produced by Chetna Organic, a cooperative of small family farms. PACT will be supporting a variety of social projects in cotton growing villages to help build strong and vibrant communities. No pesticides, no fertilizers, no bleaches, no sweatshops, no nasty stuff at all. PACT promises you premium organic cotton and other sustainable textiles ethically made so you not only feel good in PACT but feel good about where PACT came from",[],PACT Women's Organic Cotton Dove Grey Fair Isle Tights,"<div class=""a-section a-spacing-small"" id=""variation_size_name"">

column8: Maxi skirts are a wardrobe staple for most of us during the spring and summer, but they can also be worn during the fall and winter as well. That’s what’s so great about them – they’re versatile, easy to style with anything, and incredibly comfy. If you didn’t buy one yet, you need to for spring, because there are so many outfits you can create with one.

Wear your maxi skirt with a crop top. Wear it higher on your waist so you show very little skin, or wear it lower to bare your stomach. Whatever you’re comfortable with. Layer a blazer over a tee and maxi skirt for an easy fall or winter look or Kick your outfit up a notch by layering with a jean jacket. This is great for fall or spring.
MATERIAL & CARE INSTRUCTIONS: MADE IN USA with premium soft stretch fabric ( 95% Rayon / 5% Spandex ). Hand Wash or Machine Wash Cold Delicate Cycle / Hang Dry
Model is 5' 6"" and wearing size Small

column8: Hand Wash Cold or Dry Clean

If edgy is your style, then this cool, sexy denim PU leather zip sleeves blazer jacket is what you need. It features PU leather panels and zipper detailing on the back of the sleeves, giving it its biker chic look.
In the middle part of this edgy, denim biker coat is a hook and eye closure. It also comes with a full lining to keep you warm on a cold day.

What makes this amazing contrast blazer a real treasure to keep in your collection is that you can either dress it up or down. Team it up with a dress to put some edge into your look. Or pair it with a tank top and jeans for a cool weekend style.
If you want a contemporary look, this cool biker coat with PU sleeves and pleated design surely fits the bill perfectly. It comes in three colors: grey, green and army green.

Whether you're going for a foxy, edgy or casual chic look, this beautiful women blazer would definitely be a fantastic choice. This comes in sizes 2 to 14.",[],Lookbook Store Women's Denim PU Leather Zip Sleeves Pleated Tuxedo Blazer Jacket,"<div class=""a-section a-spacing-small"" id=""variation_size_name"">

column8: MADE IN THE USA - High quality is synonymous with close attention to detail, that can only be achieved with local manufacturing. Feel confident knowing you're supporting an innovative American business.

DURABLE - The patented elastic strap is tested to be the longest lasting, most comfortable on the market. Shirt Stay Plus is designed to be worn daily and withstand washing. Metal clasps with nylon teeth firmly grip your shirts all day without damaging them. SSP has been proven to succeed by thousands of professionals worldwide.
ADJUSTABLE - Our shirt stays are designed to fit you. They have a lot of play to ensure a perfect fit and a shirt tucked in comfortably all day long.

CHOOSE A STYLE - Choose from a) THE ORIGINALS which include 4 straight shirt stay, with 2 on each side connecting your sock and shirt, b) THE STIRRUPS which include 2 stays, with which you slide your foot through a loop at the bottom and two clips on each stay connect to your shirt, c) THE ""Y-STYLE"" which is our most popular and includes 2 stays where each stay has one clip connecting to your sock and two clips connecting to your shirt.",[],Worlds Best Shirt Stays - Select Series by Shirt Stay Plus,

column8: ADVANCED TECHNOLOGY: This Columbia Men's Watertight II Jacket features Omni-Tech waterproof breathable seam-sealed construction for guaranteed protection during rain heavy days outside.
HANDY FEATURES: This waterproof rain jacket features zippered hand pockets, an abrasion resistant chin guard, a drop tail, and a packable contruction for convenience and efficiency.

Enjoy Xero Shoes for walking, hiking, biking, yoga, working out, paddle boarding, water sports, jogging, running, and even 100-mile ultra marathons.
5.5mm non-marking, non-slip, FeelTrue sole for total natural movement with just-right protection. The only outsole made specifically for barefoot-style sandals.
Patent-pending, easy-adjust lacing holds comfortably on your foot without pressure points common in flip-flops.
Lightweight and flexible enough to fit in your pocket, pack or purse. Soles have a 5,000 mile warranty

NOTE: To guarantee a correct fit, please measure your foot: 1) Place a piece of paper on the floor, against a wall; 2) Step on the paper, your heel against the wall; 3) Mark the paper in line with your longest toe; 4) Measure that length with a ruler; 5) Compare that length to the sizing chart (link, above).
